==Trivia==
*Sylvie Laufeydottir is an amalgamation of different characters from the comics:
**'''[[Loki]]''', who temporarily reincarnated into a female after being killed during [[Ragnarök]].
**'''Sylvie Lushton''', a [[human]] girl magically enhanced by [[Loki]], who became the second known '''Enchantress''', modelling her appearance after the first one, the [[Asgardian]] [[Amora]].
*Sylvie Laufeydottir wears an [[Wikipedia:Ankh|ankh]] as an earring.
*Before revealing her name to be "Sylvie," Laufeydottir is only referred to by Audio Description as the "Blond Variant."

==Behind the Scenes==
*Laufeydottir's costume was made by [[Christine Wada]], who added concealed zippers to facilitate [[Sophia Di Martino]] nursing her baby between takes.<ref>[https://twitter.com/sophiadimartino/status/1410512718952607744 Sophia Di Martino on Twitter]</ref>
*[[Sarah Irwin]] and [[Maureen Lavoyer]] were stunt doubles for [[Sophia Di Martino]] in the role of Sylvie Laufeydottir.

